Class ShowCaseSequenceItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • bean.pwr.imskamieskiego.GUI.showcase.ShowCaseSequenceItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.elconfidencial.bubbleshowcase.BubbleShowCaseListener

    public class ShowCaseSequenceItem
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.elconfidencial.bubbleshowcase.BubbleShowCaseListener
    This class is a wrapper for BubbleShowCase. This wrapper with ShowCaseSequence class are hack for BubbleShowCase sequence limitations like for ex. inability to finish sequence, when back button is pressed.
